  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a robata grill over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the lamb mince and cook until browned, breaking it up into small pieces.",
    "Add the onion, ginger, garliic, and red chili pepper to the grill and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, turmeric, and paprika to the grill and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the coconut milk to the grill and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 20 minutes.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or with naan bread."
